{"type": "article", "id": 23674, "title": "现代感的茶叶包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-11T08:24:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113106sE1I8FRJxmLB9dkV.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组茶叶包装的亮点在配色，相互之间区分度很高且有很强的撞击感，比如绿色配橙色，红色配蓝色，新鲜而潮流。每个包装上都是一个带吸管的茶杯图案，用不同的颜色突出吸管，引起人们喝的欲望。整体包装上都有排列整齐的黑色圆点，增加了年轻和潮流的气息。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071131036g0cAeSIWKnYqiJ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113104vaOAbgTG965DeSfR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113104TPBInSZM9mVwyDcl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113105ujmgaBeTv62EL9Kf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}